m/artists/kiss">亲吻</a>更具破坏性。他们还没有看到性手枪……在自己的祖国被禁止，英格兰的性手枪否认了对美国的入场费 - 性手枪将新浪的新浪潮带到了Longhorn宴会厅。</p><p>查找下面的详细信息，然后<a href="https://store.sexpistolsofficial.com/collections/music?utm_source=PressRelease&amp;utm_campaign=SexPistols20241216&amp;utm_medium=referral&amp;utm_referrer=direct&amp;utm_board=umc-uk-catalogue&amp;utm_country=GB&amp;utm_linkurl=SexPistols.lnk.to%2FliveintheUSA&amp;lf=d87bda88e51d17a28d27509435344c29" target="_blank" rel="noopener">访问此处进行预订</a>。 </p><figure id="attachment_3828808" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828808" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828808" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sex-pistols-San-Fran@2000x1270.jpg" alt="Sex Pistols的“ Live in USA 1978”盒装：旧金山。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sex-pistols-San-Fran@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sex-pistols-San-Fran@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sex-pistols-San-Fran@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sex-pistols-San-Fran@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sex-pistols-San-Fran@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sex-pistols-San-Fran@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3828808" class="wp-caption-text"> Sex Pistols的“ Live in USA 1978”盒装：旧金山。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><figure id="attachment_3828807" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3828807" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3828807" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/sex-pistols-Atlanta@2000x1270.jpg" alt="性手枪的“ 1978年美国生活”盒子：亚特兰大。" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/202